INTELLIGENT SQL QUERYING USING LLMs (Gemini Pro)
Submission Date: February 2026
ABSTRACT
This project presents an Intelligent SQL Querying System powered by Large Language Models (LLMs) using Gemini Pro. The system enables users to query relational databases using natural language instead of writing SQL commands manually. The model converts user questions into structured SQL queries, validates them, and executes them securely on the database. This improves accessibility, reduces technical barriers, and enhances productivity.
